<paragraph id="8B95D74C37571B77FF5E47F2FCEDED3F" blockId="20.[192,1440,194,698]" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">
The three views of the 
<typeStatus id="549169EE37571B77FDBD47F2FDF5EEBC" box="[531,636,418,442]" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">holotype</typeStatus>
specimen (dorsal habitus, lateral habitus, and close-up of head) provided by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBBAABD37571B77FEFF4792FD50EEDC" author="Rodrigues, J. M. D. S. &amp; J. R. M. Mermudes" box="[337,729,450,474]" pageId="20" pageNumber="19" pagination="44 - 48" refId="ref13056" refString="Rodrigues, J. M. D. S., and J. R. M. Mermudes. 2011. A new species of Peritrox Bates, with a revised key for the genus (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae, Lamiinae). Zootaxa 3000: 44 - 48." type="journal article" year="2011">Rodrigues and Mermudes (2011)</bibRefCitation>
indicate the eyes of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2AACCF37571B77FC694792FBDEEEDC" authorityName="Rodrigues and Mermudes" authorityYear="2011" box="[967,1111,450,474]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Peritrox" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="insulatus">
<emphasis id="B95E0B5E37571B77FC694792FBDEEEDC" box="[967,1111,450,474]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">P. insulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are moderately large; frons approximately subquadrate, about as wide as 2 1/2 lower eye lobe widths; genae a little shorter than lower eye lobes, about 3/4 as tall; antennal tubercles unarmed, moderately separated, not contiguous at base; scape clavate, not gradually expanded to apex.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B95D74C37571B77FF5E4412FCABEDBC" blockId="20.[192,1440,194,698]" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">
Based on these morphological differences, the specimen described by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBBAABD37571B77FBF34412FE84ED7C" author="Rodrigues, J. M. D. S. &amp; J. R. M. Mermudes" pageId="20" pageNumber="19" pagination="44 - 48" refId="ref13056" refString="Rodrigues, J. M. D. S., and J. R. M. Mermudes. 2011. A new species of Peritrox Bates, with a revised key for the genus (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae, Lamiinae). Zootaxa 3000: 44 - 48." type="journal article" year="2011">Rodrigues and Mermudes (2011)</bibRefCitation>
conforms more closely to characteristics of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C2AACCF37571B77FC374432FB20ED7C" authority="Thomson" authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1860" box="[921,1193,610,634]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Ischiocentra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B95E0B5E37571B77FC374432FBA6ED7C" box="[921,1071,610,634]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">Ischiocentra</emphasis>
Thomson
</taxonomicName>
, known from 
<collectingCountry id="F33D97DC37571B77FAE34432FA12ED7C" box="[1357,1435,610,634]" name="Brazil" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F33D97DC37571B77FF6E44D2FEBEED9C" box="[192,311,642,666]" name="Colombia" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">Colombia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F33D97DC37571B77FEED44D2FE43ED9C" box="[323,458,642,666]" name="Costa Rica" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">Costa Rica</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F33D97DC37571B77FE7844D2FDB6ED9F" box="[470,575,642,665]" name="Panama" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">Panama</collectingCountry>
, and 
<collectingCountry id="F33D97DC37571B77FD2F44D2FC8CED9C" box="[641,773,642,666]" name="Venezuela" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
. Therefore, we propose the 
<emphasis id="B95E0B5E37571B77FBF944D2FACFED9F" bold="true" box="[1111,1350,641,666]" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">new combination</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C2AACCF37571B77FAE044D2FC97EDBC" authority="(Rodrigues and Mermudes, 2011)" baseAuthorityName="Rodrigues and Mermudes" baseAuthorityYear="2011" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Ischiocentra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="insulata">
<emphasis id="B95E0B5E37571B77FAE044D2FEF3EDBC" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">Ischiocentra insulata</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFBBAABD37571B77FE2444F2FC9CEDBC" author="Rodrigues, J. M. D. S. &amp; J. R. M. Mermudes" box="[394,789,674,698]" pageId="20" pageNumber="19" pagination="44 - 48" refId="ref13056" refString="Rodrigues, J. M. D. S., and J. R. M. Mermudes. 2011. A new species of Peritrox Bates, with a revised key for the genus (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae, Lamiinae). Zootaxa 3000: 44 - 48." type="journal article" year="2011">Rodrigues and Mermudes, 2011</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
